#: ../../Y/Yet-Another.rst:5
msgid "Yet Another"
msgstr "Yet Another"

#: ../../Y/Yet-Another.rst:7
msgid "adj\\."
msgstr "形容詞"

#: ../../Y/Yet-Another.rst:9
msgid ""
"[From Unix's :manpage:`yacc(1)`\\, ‘Yet Another Compiler-Compiler’, a LALR "
"parser generator]"
msgstr ""
"[Unixの\\ :manpage:`yacc(1)`\\ 、‘Yet Another Compiler-"
"Compiler’というLALR構文解析器生成器から]"

#: ../../Y/Yet-Another.rst:12
msgid ""
"Of your own work: A humorous allusion often used in titles to acknowledge "
"that the topic is not original, though the content is. As in ‘Yet Another AI"
" Group’ or ‘Yet Another Simulated Annealing Algorithm’."
msgstr ""
"自分自身の仕事について: そのトピックが、内容は独自であっても、独創的ではないと認めるために、しばしばタイトルに使われるユーモラスな言及。‘Yet "
"Another AI Group’や‘Yet Another Simulated Annealing Algorithm’のように。"

#: ../../Y/Yet-Another.rst:16
msgid ""
"Of others' work: Describes something of which there are already far too "
"many. See also :ref:`YA-`\\, :ref:`YABA`\\, :ref:`YAUN`\\."
msgstr ""
"他人の仕事について: すでに数が多すぎる類のものを表す。\\ :ref:`YA-`\\ 、\\ :ref:`YABA`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`YAUN`\\ も参照。"
